cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the robustness of 3D representations and deep networks in critical vision tasks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of adversarial attacks and defense mechanisms is also a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper proposes novel attack operations and detection schemes, which are related to neural networks (cs.NE).
